{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479", "id": 68783774, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU2ODc4Mzc3NA==", "number": 24479, "title": "TLS dtor panics abort the process", "user": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 43009118, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw0MzAwOTExOA==", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-destructors", "name": "A-destructors", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: destructors (Drop, ..)"}, {"id": 211668062, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMTE2NjgwNjI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-libs-api", "name": "T-libs-api", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the library API team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}, {"id": 632886930, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2MzI4ODY5MzA=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-thread-locals", "name": "A-thread-locals", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Thread local storage (TLS)"}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2015-04-15T20:47:20Z", "updated_at": "2021-01-25T03:16:11Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Today a destructor in TLS which panics will abort the process:\n\n``` rust\nstruct Foo;\n\nimpl Drop for Foo {\n    fn drop(&mut self) { panic!() }\n}\n\nthread_local!(static FOO: Foo = Foo);\n\npub fn main() {\n    FOO.with(|_| {});\n}\n```\n\nWhen compiled and run (note that it must be run on a recent system due to #19776):\n\n```\nthread '<main>' panicked at 'explicit panic', foo.rs:4\nfatal runtime error: Could not unwind stack, error = 5\nzsh: illegal hardware instruction  ./foo\n```\n\nThe reason behind this is that the context in which TLS destructors are running is different than the execution of the main thread itself (e.g. there is no try/catch block).\n\nIs this (a) desirable and (b) should we change it?\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/24479/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}